## Comparison with Creative Commons

Software Commons is like [Creative Commons][9] for software. Creative Commons
is explicitly [_not_ for software][10], but encompasses a range of sharing
practices for creative works. The Creative Commons motto is, &ldquo;[Some
rights reserved][11],&rdquo; and it includes licenses that [restrict commercial
use][12], and licenses that [restrict modification][13]. Software Commons
encompasses a similar breadth of sharing practices for software.

